race.comment: COOLABAH STATION (1) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fourth (26.12) last time in a Special conditions H at Geelong. Form at the trip excellent including two wins. Better than last start and worth following up. WEBLEC BILLY (4) had the drop on the lead before drawing clear to score (29.96) at this track in Grade 5 over 525m. Has definite claims. QUEEN KIMETTO (2) could manage only third at this track last time but impressed when posting a strong 29.99 over 525m at this track three starts ago. Rates a leading chance if runs up to recent winning time. WHIPPING IT (3) can measure up with the right run.
